name: CL9 Compressor/Limiter
details:
Classic Compressor / LimiterThe CL9 smooths out your signal stopping ear-piercing volume peaks and boosting low-level bass strings. It gives you a very even tone across the entire spectrum and delivers killer sustain. Dial in the Attack and Sustain knobs to get that perfect sound for guitar or bass. 
-Compressor evens out your sound and adds sustain
-Attack and Sustain knobs shape your sound and the pedals reaction time
-Smooth out string volume and unwanted volume peaks
-Give your clean sound punch and a percussive edge
